		"description": "<p>You never stop innovating, whether it&rsquo;s new arms and armor, new supplemental tricks, or even new fighting techniques. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Your Strength, Dexterity, or Intelligence score increases by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li>\n<li>You gain an additional maneuver of a level you could learn from the combat tradition you selected as part of Combat Gadgeteer.</li>\n<li>When a spell invention you are using fizzles, you can immediately use your reaction to turn it into an impromptu explosive device and throw it at a space within 30 feet, where it explodes, dealing a number of six-sided dice of force damage equal to your proficiency bonus in a 10-foot radius. Creatures in this radius can make a Dexterity saving throw against your artificer spell save DC, taking half damage on a successful save. This utterly destroys the spell invention, however, and it cannot be repaired, but must be replaced.</li>\n</ul>",
